description: RARELY AVAILABLE ~ Stunning, upper level condo with breathtaking, panoramic water views in the exclusive 50 Liberty Waterfront Residences! Boasting extra high ceilings and exceptional floor plan, this special unit offers sophisticated living with floor-to-ceiling windows that flood the space with natural light showcasing the beautiful finishes and exceptional ocean & harbor views. Gourmet kitchen features custom high-gloss lacquer cabinets, professional appliances, and a waterfall island. Wake up to ocean views in the primary suite with spa-like ensuite marble bath. The second bedroom has marina views and a fresh modern bath. Unwind on the private balcony, taking in the picturesque surroundings. Two prime adjacent garage parking spots, one with an EV charger. Don't miss the opportunity to experience the epitome of luxury living, close to the Seaports’ finest restaurants & boutiques, where every detail has been carefully curated to provide the ultimate in upscale urban living!
